<p>Okay brilliant, we can see both â€˜/etc/apache2â€™ and â€˜~â€™ are in our stack! The directory stack is a last in first out stack, meaning anything you place on the stack will come off in exactly that order, like a stack of plates.</p>

<p>If we run popd at this point, itâ€™ll take us back to our home directory:</p>

